content.task: Validate final CI pipeline fix after resolving sphinx dependency conflict. Provide comprehensive assessment of all pipeline status and recommend next steps for production readiness validation.
content.context: We have successfully fixed multiple CI pipeline issues: 1) Main CI now passes completely (✅ all 16 unit tests, integration tests, security scans, performance tests), 2) Fixed requirements-dev.txt conflicts including sphinx version compatibility, 3) Multi-agent system confirmed operational via MCP. Need final validation before declaring CI pipeline fully operational.
